aṅguttara nikāya 10
15. ariyavagga
149. uppādetabbasutta
“uppādetabbañca vo, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ desessāmi na uppādetabbañca.
taṃ suṇātha … pe …
katamo ca, bhikkhave, na uppādetabbo dhammo?
micchādiṭṭhi … pe … micchāvimutti—
ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, na uppādetabbo dhammo.
katamo ca, bhikkhave, uppādetabbo dhammo?
sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāvimutti—
ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, uppādetabbo dhammo”ti.
pañcamaṃ.
